    * `:fill` — gap-fill policy, one of `#{inspect(@valid_fill)}` (default `:nil`)
    * `:allowed_lateness` — non-negative integer milliseconds (default `0`)

  Raises `ArgumentError` for an invalid `interval_ms` or invalid options.
  """
